description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 162, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [162 Votes, Top 10% Score]
